                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8802" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0271</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">845 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">佤乡新歌，幸福落地——东方航空战略性企业社会责任的践行之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">New Song of Wa Town, Happiness on the Ground - Eastern Airline&#39;s Strategic Corporate Social Responsibility Practices</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王颖晖，廖茂君，齐悦童，权钺</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东航技术应用研发中心有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略性企业社会责任；企业公民；产业扶贫；乡村振兴；东航扶贫模式；可持续竞争优势</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Strategic corporate social responsibility, Corporate citizenship, Industrial poverty alleviation, Rural revitalization, China Eastern Airlines poverty alleviation model,Sustainable competitive advantage</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国的扶贫事业是彰显了社会主义国家政治优势的伟大社会实践，激发了广泛的社会关注和动员，唤醒了深藏于企业血脉里的社会责任心和使命感，企业通过发挥积极性、主动性、创造性，举企业之力，服从中央指挥，配合市场动力，在中国特色行动中发挥着重要作用。本案例详细探讨了中国东方航空公司如何运用其航空业务优势，将扶贫目标纳入战略发展规划中，以科学方式精准聚焦、精准发力，追贫困之根，溯致贫之源，解贫困之惑，为云南省沧源、双江两县的脱贫攻坚工作做出了突出贡献。同时，东方航空依托当地资源、立足市场需求、把握政策机遇，通过航空、产业和消费三大扶贫方式，采取了企业内外联动的机制，促进了乡村振兴战略的可持续实施。东方航空承担战略性社会责任不仅践行了作为央企的使命担当，为企业长期发展赢得了可持续竞争优势，同时也为其他企业如何更好履行社会责任提供了借鉴和启示。本案例旨在帮助学生理解企业战略性社会责任内涵、驱动因素、履责方式以及企业公民等相关理论与方法，启发学生开展对企业如何将社会责任与企业战略融合，实现长期双赢的深度思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">China&#39;s poverty alleviation is a great social practice that highlights the political advantages of the socialist state, inspires widespread social concern and mobilization, and awakens the social responsibility and sense of mission deeply embedded in the blood of enterprises, which, by exercising their activism, initiative, and creativity, lift up their corporate strength, obey the command of the central government, and cooperate with the market dynamics, and play an important role in the action of China&#39;s characteristics. This case discusses in detail how China Eastern Airlines utilized its aviation business advantages to incorporate poverty alleviation goals into its strategic development planning, focusing and focusing precisely in a scientific manner, chasing the root of poverty, tracing the source of poverty, and solving the problem of poverty, and making outstanding contributions to poverty alleviation efforts in Cangyuan、Shuangjiang counties in Yunnan Province. At the same time, relying on local resources, based on market demand, and grasping policy opportunities, China Eastern Airlines has adopted a mechanism of internal and external linkage through the three major ways of poverty alleviation, namely aviation, industry and consumption, to promote the sustainable implementation of the strategy of rural revitalization. China Eastern Airline&#39;s strategic social responsibility not only fulfills its mission as a centralized enterprise and wins a sustainable competitive advantage for the long-term development of the enterprise, but also provides reference and inspiration for other enterprises on how to better fulfill their social responsibility. This case aims to help students understand the connotation of strategic social responsibility, driving factors, ways of fulfillment, and corporate citizenship and other related theories and methods, and inspire students to carry out in-depth thinking on how to integrate social responsibility and corporate strategy to achieve a long-term win-win situation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略性企业社会责任；社会责任金字塔模型；企业公民理论；利益相关者理论；产业价值链理论；企业资源理论；可持续竞争优势理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
